OL,3,CMurals, stadium tours, and loyal fans:
OL,4,CInside Erling Haaland's hometown
OL,6,FWe are on safari in Norway... the
OL,7,FErling Haaland safari to be precise.
OL,9,F"You can score a goal where Erling
OL,10,FHaaland scored a goal," tour guide
OL,11,FGeir Magnus Sandve tells us.
OL,13,FTwice a week, Sandve and his
OL,14,Fcolleagues show people around Bryne
OL,15,FFK, the hometown football club where
OL,16,FHaaland played from the age of five.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
