OL,3,CMurals, stadium tours, and loyal fans:
OL,4,CInside Erling Haaland's hometown
OL,6,FThe tours started after the 25-year-
OL,7,Fold Norwegian striker made history by
OL,8,Fwinning the treble - three major
OL,9,Ftrophies in a single season - with
OL,10,FManchester City in 2023.
OL,12,FThree years on, Haaland continues to
OL,13,Fmake history, but this time with the
OL,14,FNorwegian men's football team, who
OL,15,Fwill play in their first-ever World
OL,16,FCup quarterfinals, against England on
OL,17,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
