OL,3,CMurals, stadium tours, and loyal fans:
OL,4,CInside Erling Haaland's hometown
OL,6,FHow does Erling Haaland think he
OL,7,Fcompares to Harry Kane? Good Morning
OL,8,FBritain's Ashna Hurynag asks the
OL,9,FNorwegian striker himself
OL,11,FSandve's colleague, Endre Refnes, a
OL,12,Fvolunteer in his 70s, tells us:
OL,13,F"Tourists want to know lots of things
OL,14,Fand we try and answer them."
OL,16,FIn the dressing room, we are shown
OL,17,Fpictures of six-year-old Haaland - a
OL,18,Flittle boy, short in height and slight
OL,19,Fin frame. A far cry from the 6ft 4
OL,20,Fgiant of a centre-forward we are more
OL,21,Ffamiliar with.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@\O]
