OL,3,CMurals, stadium tours, and loyal fans:
OL,4,CInside Erling Haaland's hometown
OL,6,F"He was very little until he was about
OL,7,F12 or 13, and then at about 15 or 16
OL,8,Fhe went away to Molde, and his mother
OL,9,Fwas a cook, and she was feeding him,"
OL,10,FRefnes says.
OL,12,F"He grew about 20cm in height in about
OL,13,Fone, one-and-a-half years. And then
OL,14,Fthe muscle came."
OL,16,FWe also speak to his youth team coach,
OL,17,FEspen Undheim, who tells me how unique
OL,18,FHaaland was, even at the age of nine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
