OL,3,CMurals, stadium tours, and loyal fans:
OL,4,CInside Erling Haaland's hometown
OL,6,F"What was special about him was his
OL,7,Fhunger for always being a striker,"
OL,8,Fsays Undheim. "He always tried to find
OL,9,Fthe gap between defenders, to be in
OL,10,Fthe right position in front of the
OL,11,Fgoal."
OL,13,F"His mindset was, 'Where can I be for
OL,14,Fscoring goals?' No one else had the
OL,15,Fsame kind of instinct, and I have
OL,16,Fnever seen it since."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@cO]xD@UO]
