OL,3,CMurals, stadium tours, and loyal fans:
OL,4,CInside Erling Haaland's hometown
OL,6,FBryne, a town of less than 20,000
OL,7,Fpeople, has giant murals of Haaland
OL,8,Feverywhere - whenever the striker
OL,9,Fmoves to a new club, a new mural is
OL,10,Fpainted.
OL,12,FOne of him in a Borussia Dortmund
OL,13,Fshirt is plastered across the side of
OL,14,Fa building almost 50ft high.
OL,16,FIt goes without saying that a trip to
OL,17,Fthe murals is an integral part of the
OL,18,FHaaland safari.
OL,20,FThe locals are delighted with the
OL,21,Fworldwide interest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
