OL,3,CMurals, stadium tours, and loyal fans:
OL,4,CInside Erling Haaland's hometown
OL,6,F"He went to school with my son for 10
OL,7,Fyears, just a normal boy, and now he's
OL,8,Fa global superstar," one woman tells
OL,9,Fus.
OL,11,F"We love him and we own him, all of us
OL,12,Fin Bryne, he is ours," beams another.
OL,14,FWhen Haaland lines up against England
OL,15,Fon Saturday, Bryne's stadium will be
OL,16,Ffull with supporters watching the
OL,17,Fmatch on a big screen.
OL,19,FEvery one of them is willing to write
OL,20,Ftheir very own Viking into history.
